high_descs: Turn right and take one step, then turn left and walk across the room, then turn left to face the desk.
Pick up the pencil near the edge of the desk.
Turn around and take one step, then turn back around to face the desk.
Put the pencil down directly in front of the set of books on the left.
anns.task_desc: Move the pencil to a different area of the desk.

high_descs: Go to the right side of the wooden desk in front of you.
Pick up the white pencil on the desk.
Turn around and look behind you and then turn back around.
Place the white pencil on the desk near the books.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the white pencil on the desk and put it on another spot on the desk.

high_descs: Walk forward and left to face the desk.
Pick up the white pencil from the desk.
Put the white pencil down on the desk close to the standing books on the lower left side.
anns.task_desc: Move a pencil farther back on the desk.
